'''法蒂玛之手'''（{{lang-ar|خمسة}} ''khamsah''，即“五”）是[[西亚|西亚]]以及[[北非|北非]]地区常见的一种掌型护身符，在[[珠宝|珠宝]]店和室内挂饰中很常見<ref name=Bernasekp12>Bernasek et al., 2008, [http://books.google.ca/books?id=584VAQAAIAAJ&q=khamsa+%22middle+east%22+%22north+africa%22&dq=khamsa+%22middle+east%22+%22north+africa%22&hl=en&ei=_imrTe6mEMeSswbg7uSZCA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CD4Q6AEwBDgK p. 12] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=584VAQAAIAAJ&q=khamsa+%22middle+east%22+%22north+africa%22&dq=khamsa+%22middle+east%22+%22north+africa%22&hl=en&ei=_imrTe6mEMeSswbg7uSZCA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CD4Q6AEwBDgK |date=20141021131839 }}.</ref><ref name=Sonbolp355>Sonbol, 2005, [http://books.google.ca/books?id=uUe8tBUvwE4C&pg=PA355&dq=%22hand+of+fatima%22+evil+eye&hl=en&ei=_NyrTaeKNsrZsgaAm9j7Bg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CDoQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=%22hand%20of%20fatima%22%20evil%20eye&f=false pp. 355-359] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=uUe8tBUvwE4C&pg=PA355&dq=%22hand+of+fatima%22+evil+eye&hl=en&ei=_NyrTaeKNsrZsgaAm9j7Bg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CDoQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=%22hand%20of%20fatima%22%20evil%20eye&f=false |date=20180707173833 }}.</ref>。穆斯林认为这一手掌为先知[[穆罕默德|穆罕默德]]之女[[法蒂玛|法蒂玛]]的右手，因此得名。法蒂玛之手在历史上对许多社区进行保护，[[傳統|傳統]]认为它可以防护[[邪眼|邪恶之眼]]。在黎凡特（Levantine，指叙利亚、黎巴嫩、巴勒斯坦和约旦地区）的基督教徒中，这一护身符被称为“玛丽之手”，玛丽指[[耶稣|耶稣]]基督之圣母[[玛利亚|玛利亚]]；而[[犹太人|犹太人]]也逐渐开始使用这一标志，称为“米利暗之手”，[[米利暗|米利暗]]指先知[[摩西|摩西]]之姐。

